🔹 Identity:-
getRiskScore()
setRiskScore(int riskScore)

🔹 Role (Bundle):-
getRiskScore()
setRiskScore(int riskScore)
getRiskScoreWeight()
setRiskScoreWeight(int weight)

🔹 Entitlement (ManagedAttribute):-
getRiskScore()
setRiskScore(int riskScore)

🔹 Related (Risk Calculation Support):-
getPolicyViolations()
setPolicyViolations(java.util.List violations)
getRoles()
setRoles(java.util.List roles)
getLinks()
setLinks(java.util.List links)
getEntitlements()
setEntitlements(java.util.List entitlements)

🔹 Custom / Rule Based (User-defined):-
calculateRiskScore()
updateRiskScore()
