System.out.println(weight);
✅ Output:-
30
🧠 Matlab:-
👉 Ye role total risk me 30% contribute karega

6. setRiskScoreWeight(int weight):-
👉 Role ka weight set karta hai
role.setRiskScoreWeight(40);
✅ Output:-
Role Weight = 40%
