🔥 🔹 getEntitlements():-
👉 User ke paas kaun-kaun se access/group hai
java.util.List ents = identity.getEntitlements();
System.out.println(ents);

✅ Output:-
[Admins, Finance_Read, HR_Write]
🧠 Matlab:-
👉 Har entitlement ka risk hota hai → final RiskScore me add hota hai.

🔹 setEntitlements(List entitlements):-
👉 User ke entitlements set karta hai
identity.setEntitlements(entList);
